      <h1>1594 装备，技术，人才我们都要抢（29/30）</h1> 
      <div class="info">
       <span>作者：葫芦村人</span>
       <a href="/txt55913/" title="返回《超级军工帝国》介绍页" id="book55913">超级军工帝国</a> 本章字节数:6081065
       <script type="text/javascript">article_nav('55913','18864456');</script> 
       <a href="http://www.80txt.com/txtxz/55913.html" class="txt" id="down55913">超级军工帝国txt下载</a>
